{"tid":2065053,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"屌你老母！！！以內地假學歷入職關員　男子獲判社服令","createTime":"2020-06-15T09:06:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T02:50:26.000Z","uid":213877,"like":10,"dislike":143,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"af8b4d6916a482d06ddacc3e7b5bd146870b7b6b","tid":2065053,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:06:26.000Z","msg":"<strong>以內地假學歷入職關員 男子獲判社服令<br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200615/bkn-20200615115357043-0615_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200615%2Fbkn-20200615115357043-0615_00822_001.html&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7tAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=dd6a1ab1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200615/bkn-20200615115357043-0615_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200615/photo/bkn-20200615115357043-0615_00822_001_01p.jpg?20200615115401\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200615%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200615115357043-0615_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20200615115401&h=b10e7d35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林天鵬用假學歷到海關應徵，獲判社會服務令。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n25歲男子用800元人民幣在內地購得兩張虛假的內地大學英語考試成績報告，成功欺騙香港學術及職業資歷評審局和香港海關，更獲聘為海關關員，其後才被匿名信揭發，他在受僱的半年期間，獲發約14萬港元薪金。他早前承認兩項使用虛假文書副本罪，今（15日）在東區法院判刑。裁判官香淑嫻指他有真誠悔意，加上承諾會還款予海關，決定給他機會，判他160小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n25歲被告林天鵬，被控於2017年8月16日及2018年1月4日，明知一張據稱由中華人民共和國高等教育部發出的大學英語四級考試成績報告單，以及一張全國大學英語六級考試成績報告單屬虛假，而使用該文書的副本，意圖使香港學術及職業資歷評審局及香港海關接受為真文書副本。<br />\n<br />\n案情顯示，被告於2017年8月16日，用電郵將上述兩張虛假的內地大學英語學歷寄予香港學術及職業資歷評審局，以申請本港學歷認證，評審局其後向被告發出相等於香港文憑試5科合格的成績認證。被告於2017年10月以該認申請海關關員一職，並成功獲聘。"},{"pid":"a00d8a7bebf2f4063c40120a93172b952e30ecea","tid":2065053,"uid":213877,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:06:39.000Z","msg":"社會服務令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd7032c83850bd6884a9b75d4051d3b29c32a99","tid":2065053,"uid":230104,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:09:03.000Z","msg":"見到個法官名，大概估到點判"},{"pid":"254fe1052e16b34eea1a26f03201dcaa0436f813","tid":2065053,"uid":199479,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:10:34.000Z","msg":"唔好再請大陸學歷嘅人咪得囉"},{"pid":"861fcec0318e319103c54704bbd4216fb539a649","tid":2065053,"uid":213877,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"254fe1052e16b34eea1a26f03201dcaa0436f813","tid":2065053,"uid":199479,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:10:34.000Z","msg":"唔好再請大陸學歷嘅人咪得囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:11:11.000Z","msg":"重點係社會服務令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b75c84c7709e64b5c49286b57bbfff85da3a514d","tid":2065053,"uid":72173,"like":74,"dislike":2,"score":72,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:12:14.000Z","msg":"虛假文書過往幾時有咁輕判過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時最少幾年加案底<br />\n<br />\n平時又話乜撚野阻嚇性重罰<br />\n大陸西就服務令<br />\n<br />\n既然咁小事咁無人怕你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支持大家小學畢業印兩張野入去"},{"pid":"60a176dba129ff0f9b70b80812340d01d2077ee0","tid":2065053,"uid":23993,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:13:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香淑嫻</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1ec216bf3ebc8945c50b5c8d3cbf3e93202c6ff0","tid":2065053,"uid":112748,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:14:57.000Z","msg":"高尚情操花巨款購買證書加入海關為香港市民服務"},{"pid":"8ba632589553ca135c6e3dfd131628c4a07f87c0","tid":2065053,"uid":103156,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T09:16:22.000Z","msg":"博得過喎，刑罰咁低！冇人揭發，根本一世都冇人知。"},{"pid":"01541adc13c8e6f7c56